						<p>This fragmentary inscription, of which the date portion is lost, probably records a grant of 12 <hi rend="italic">achchu</hi> of money by a person or persons (name not preserved) for the decoration <hi rend="italic">(tiru-mēlpūchchu),</hi> evidently of a deity (name not preserved).</p>						

